title: 2014–15 Moldovan Women's Cup
text:
The 2014–15 <a href="Moldovan%20Women%27s%20Cup">Moldovan Women's Cup</a> is the 18th edition of the <a href="Moldova">Moldova</a>n annual <a href="Association%20football">football</a> tournament. The competition began on 9 October 2014 with the Preliminary Round and will end with the final held in May 2015.
Preliminary round.
Matches took place on 9 October and 23 October 2014. Two teams have a bye to the semi-finals.
Semi-finals.
Played on 7 May and 21 May 2015.
